he premium between JTO perpetual and spot prices using their institutional-grade matching engine. The Sui-based architecture enables sub-second settlement of funding payments with minimal gas costs. Long positions pay shorts when funding is positive, reflecting market sentiment toward JTO's staking yield potential. Bluefin's order book model provides transparent price discovery for accurate funding rate calculations."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
